# vhs script: Copilot CLI HELIX workflow integration test recording

Output INT-CP.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Shell "bash"

Type "# HELIX Workflow Integration Test: GitHub Copilot CLI"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "cd tests/workflows/copilot-cli"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# Running HELIX skill activation test with 3 scenarios"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "export GITHUB_TOKEN=<your-token>"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "bash run-scenarios.sh"
Enter
Sleep 30s
